snippet.title: Socratica
snippet.description:
Socratica makes high-quality educational videos on math and science.  
We're a couple of Caltech grads who believe you deserve better videos. You'll learn more with us!
If you like what we do, please share our videos with everyone you know!  This really helps us grow.   :)

♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥

To​ ​help​ ​us​ ​make​ ​videos more quickly,​ ​you​ ​can​ ​support​ Socratica at:

​Patreon​:
https://www.patreon.com/socratica  

Socratica Paypal:
https://www.paypal.me/socratica 
 
We also accept Bitcoin!  :)
Our​ ​address​ ​is:  1EttYyGwJmpy9bLY2UcmEqMJuBfaZ1HdG9

Here are some of our favourite products on Amazon.  Through the Amazon Influencer program, Socratica will receive a portion of each sale from this page.  
https://www.amazon.com/shop/socratica

Thank you for visiting Socratica!
